{"tid":2454720,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"焦慮症 精神科醫生 一問","createTime":"2021-03-20T12:29:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-24T11:59:37.000Z","uid":216506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8a7ced3017ce5bbadfe61ecb9ed614cdb7df358c","tid":2454720,"uid":216506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T12:29:30.000Z","msg":"講講backgroup 先：<br />\n2015 (中學) 確診焦慮症<br />\n嗰陣時 睇私人精神科 李厚道醫生<br />\n之後 因為經濟問題 叫左李醫生 寫介紹信去公立醫院睇&amp;攞藥<br />\n而私人精神科 淨係傾偈<br />\n最近，李醫生 無做返咗澳洲了<br />\n我覺得睇 公立醫院好嘥時間 (等就等半個鐘，睇就睇三分鐘)<br />\n好似咁多年都唔能夠斷尾...<br />\n<br />\n想問問<br />\n我見第二個post 都推介緊中環宋永權醫生<br />\n而且我自己21 FG，開始有經濟能力，想試下睇佢<br />\n如果唔去公立醫院覆診，交畀私家精神科醫生 跟進<br />\n會唔會有問題 ?  (e.g. 使唔使同公立醫院講？or 有咩程序？etc...)"},{"pid":"7f905fa6c69e36a0fb9b8b0d1b6a932f718f9b08","tid":2454720,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T12:32:53.000Z","msg":"我都想睇"},{"pid":"9e5d0f7dab44ad77403b20b78c257afd7172592e","tid":2454720,"uid":154255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T12:33:46.000Z","msg":"不嬲冇問題<br />\n睇邊個醫生啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你好交帶，咪去公立講聲叫佢寫張醫生紙<br />\n唔好交帶直接去睇私家都冇問題"},{"pid":"043d5eeced7124ec2822e456b2405e250c6f2bc2","tid":2454720,"uid":10820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T13:04:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1612ebf295e95418b499aecde614d7e65eace5fa","tid":2454720,"uid":216506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"043d5eeced7124ec2822e456b2405e250c6f2bc2","tid":2454720,"uid":10820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T13:04:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T13:12:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcb702007ade4ef6fcef130c9e7c8840841b49f9","tid":2454720,"uid":112205,"like":0,"disl